	- _sharesPercent = _treasury.getSharesPercentForPeriod(_userKey,_periodDate) (/unique_chucks/27/0x91a04eceece9fdb892bf5b5af77fb2564a2ba5d7.sol)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- distributionDeposits (/unique_chucks/27/0x91a04eceece9fdb892bf5b5af77fb2564a2ba5d7.sol)

	-ERC20Interface(token).transfer(_to,balance) (/unique_chucks/27/0x91a04eceece9fdb892bf5b5af77fb2564a2ba5d7.sol#156-157)

Profiterole.getTotalBonusesAmountAvailable has external calls inside a loop:
